Daniel Chang

Country Manager, PT Best World Indonesia

Mr Chang joined PT Best World Indonesia as Finance Manager in 2005 and was promoted to Deputy Country Manager in 2007, subsequently assuming the position of Country Manager in 2009. In his current role, Mr Chang has taken an executive responsibility for the development and expansion of Best World’s direct selling activities

in Indonesia. He oversees the day-to-day operations

and is in charge of sales, finance, marketing, leading business development efforts and maintaining distributor relationships in this region.

Prior to joining Best World, Mr Chang has held managerial positions with companies located in Indonesia. He holds a Bachelor’s Degree in Accounting from Trisakti University, Indonesia, and an Executive MBA degree from California State University, East Bay, USA.
